_sText: This is my first map. Please dont flame me for making it. I worked very hard on this and dont need negative feedback. I'm planning to make many more versions of this map and if you would like to help PM me and ill add you on XFIRE. This map includes 1 other fight area and 1 secret room that wont be secret for very long ;) The fish in the water under the water tower do swim! mutliple weapon pick up spots on the map. Well hope you have fun on my map and if you have suggestions on what i could do for further versions comment me!
